  "detailed_description": "Become a boss of a construction company. Demolish old houses, flatten the ground, fill foundations with concrete and build new buildings - this is what you do. Sit behind the wheel of different construction machines - from trucks and diggers to huge cranes. Win contracts and gather money to expand your company and buy or upgrade your machines.<br><br>Game Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> advanced physics and interaction with environment<br></li><li> 8 different construction machine types<br></li><li> realistic handling<br></li><li> 20 contracts to fullfill<br></li><li> additional challenges and free play mode</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Become a boss of a construction company. Demolish old houses, flatten the ground, fill foundations with concrete and build new buildings - this is what you do. Sit behind the wheel of different construction machines - from trucks and diggers to huge cranes. Win contracts and gather money to expand your company and buy or upgrade your machines.<br><br>Game Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> advanced physics and interaction with environment<br></li><li> 8 different construction machine types<br></li><li> realistic handling<br></li><li> 20 contracts to fullfill<br></li><li> additional challenges and free play mode</li></ul>",
